description:
Dabriel is playing with his array and as he is very methodical he thought that he should always know the minimum amount of elements that must be changed so that a given subarray has a value W. In other words, he wants to be able to perform two operations on his array, are they:
   1 - Change the value of the element of position X to the value W;
   2 - Inform the minimum amount of elements that need to be changed from the interval [X, Y] so that all elements have the value W.
